><strong>Issuing Organization:</strong> SAP<br>\n<strong>Credential:</strong> Professional Certification</p>\n<p>Validates skills in building and integrating generative AI solutions within the SAP ecosystem, including expertise in:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Developing AI applications on SAP Business Technology Platform (BTP)</li>\n<li>Implementing generative AI solutions using SAP AI Core</li>\n<li>Integrating LLMs and AI models into enterprise systems</li>\n<li>Working with SAP HANA Cloud and Datasphere for AI applications</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Databases and SQL for Data Science with Python (with Honors)</h2>\n<p><strong>Issuing Organization:</strong> IBM<br>\n<strong>Platform:</strong> Coursera</p>\n<p>Comprehensive certification covering:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SQL fundamentals and advanced queries</li>\n<li>Relational database design and management</li>\n<li>Data analysis using Python with SQL</li>\n<li>Working with real-world datasets</li>\n<li>Database optimization techniques</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Data Analysis with R Programming</h2>\n<p><strong>Issuing Organization:</strong> Google<br>\n<strong>Platform:</strong> Coursera</p>\n<p>Professional certification focused on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Data cleaning and transformation using R</li>\n<li>Statistical analysis and hypothesis testing</li>\n<li>Data visualization with ggplot2</li>\n<li>Reproducible research with R Markdown</li>\n<li>Real-world data analysis projects</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Let's Build the Future Together","buttonText":"Start a Conversation"},"html":"<p>Got an exciting AI project in mind? Want to collaborate on cutting-edge research? Or maybe just curious about my work? I'm all ears! Drop me a message and let's turn ideas into innovation. Coffee chats and brainstorming sessions are my favorite!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}}}